## To do list manager with notes ##

Node.js server listening for changes
JSON file for store data

new object with note
    * add title
    * add new note
    * edit note
    * delete note
    * check if done

function #1: add button creates new note
    1. open new window to type new note
        - type new title - input
        - inputs for typed text saves in JSON
        - add button
            @ add button provides new note

function #2: existing note can be modified:
    - read existing notes if they are
        - change single line of text

function #3: existing note tile expose few lines of note
    - clicked note expose bigger version of tile


